<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 06:08:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>真主党对阿鲁里之死的反应似乎“受到遏制”，交火可能会持续数月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-response-to-arouri-death-appears-contained-crossfire-could-go-on-for-months/0000018c-e096-ddba-abad-e2b7a3f00000</link><description>真主党以猛烈火箭弹和进攻性无人机进行报复。尽管对哈马斯领导人阿鲁里被暗杀的反应看似克制，但这对以色列北部流离失所的居民来说并不能带来安慰，而且可能需要几个月的时间才能希望边境恢复平静</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 04:01:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-response-to-arouri-death-appears-contained-crossfire-could-go-on-for-months/0000018c-e096-ddba-abad-e2b7a3f00000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸定居点附近疑似发生枪击事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article-live/blinken-israel-lebanon-border-is-area-of-real-concern/0000018c-e1d5-ddba-abad-e3f5e9be0000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字。 ■ 布林肯称，以色列和黎巴嫩边境是“真正令人担忧”的地区。 ■ 以色列称，哈马斯在加沙北部的军事框架已被拆除。 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 22,722 人死亡、58,166 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 03:43:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article-live/blinken-israel-lebanon-border-is-area-of-real-concern/0000018c-e1d5-ddba-abad-e3f5e9be0000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质在集会上作证：“我们遇到了遭受性虐待的人质”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-testify-at-rally-we-met-hostages-who-were-sexually-abused/0000018c-e0d0-ddba-abad-e2f10bed0000</link><description>在特拉维夫的集会上，向数千名抗议者播放了从哈马斯囚禁中返回的以色列人质的证词。罗米·科恩（Romi Cohen）的双胞胎兄弟被绑架到加沙：“我担心人们开始忘记他们。不要离开我们。时间不多了&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 23:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-testify-at-rally-we-met-hostages-who-were-sexually-abused/0000018c-e0d0-ddba-abad-e2f10bed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学撤销了八名学生的停学决定，该校声称在社交媒体上支持哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/university-reverses-suspension-of-8-students-it-claims-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-e080-daf6-a5df-e7fcbaff0000</link><description>在以色列阿拉伯少数民族权利法律中心阿达拉提出上诉后，纪律官员决定撤销暂停资格。海法大学试图让这些学生停课，声称他们的存在可能会导致“极端情况”</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 21:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/university-reverses-suspension-of-8-students-it-claims-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-e080-daf6-a5df-e7fcbaff0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布周六在加沙地带北部战斗中丧生的以色列士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-releases-name-of-israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-the-northern-gaza-strip/0000018c-e03d-daf6-a5df-e77d6f470000</link><description>31 岁的 Roee Yohay Yosef Mordechay 留下了他的妻子 Neta 和他们的小女儿 Ori，Ori 出生于犹太新年</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 20:05:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-releases-name-of-israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-the-northern-gaza-strip/0000018c-e03d-daf6-a5df-e77d6f470000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟上任一年后公布司法候选人名单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-publishes-list-of-judicial-candidates-a-year-after-taking-office/0000018c-e032-ddba-abad-e2b3136c0000</link><description>司法任命委员会将于二月和三月审查以色列各地法院的数十名未来法官</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 19:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-publishes-list-of-judicial-candidates-a-year-after-taking-office/0000018c-e032-ddba-abad-e2b3136c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议，要求举行选举并罢免内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-calling-for-elections-and-netanyahus-dismissal/0000018c-dfc8-d751-ad8d-ffec1dc00000</link><description>“政府不仅把一箱箱钱交给哈马斯，还一路卖给我们，加沙边境社区的居民。它放弃了我们，他们的谎言于 10 月 7 日在我们面前爆炸了。”加利·巴苏多 (Gali Basudo) 在特拉维夫集会上说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 19:04:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-calling-for-elections-and-netanyahus-dismissal/0000018c-dfc8-d751-ad8d-ffec1dc00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡试图推迟以色列国防军调查，以色列国家审计长开始审查军队在加沙战争中的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahu-tries-to-delay-idf-probe-state-watchdog-begins-review-of-armys-gaza-conduct/0000018c-dfc6-daf6-a5df-dffe871c0000</link><description>国家审计长马塔尼亚胡·恩格尔曼通知总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府，他将于本周开始审查与战争有关的一系列问题</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 17:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahu-tries-to-delay-idf-probe-state-watchdog-begins-review-of-armys-gaza-conduct/0000018c-dfc6-daf6-a5df-dffe871c0000</guid></item><item><title>联合国人道主义事务负责人表示，“不适宜居住”的加沙地带“饥荒即将来临”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-06/ty-article/un-humanitarian-chief-says-famine-around-the-corner-in-uninhabitable-gaza/0000018c-df45-daf6-a5df-df7dfb880000</link><description>马丁·格里菲斯还警告说，一场迫在眉睫的公共卫生灾难称，加沙为数不多的几家部分运转的医院已经不堪重负，物资严重短缺，而医疗设施遭到无情攻击，传染病正在蔓延，</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 15:33:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-06/ty-article/un-humanitarian-chief-says-famine-around-the-corner-in-uninhabitable-gaza/0000018c-df45-daf6-a5df-df7dfb880000</guid></item><item><title>真主党向以色列发射大型火箭弹，作为对哈马斯领导人被杀的“初步回应”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-fires-large-rocket-salvo-in-initial-response-to-killing-of-hamas-leader/0000018c-df37-d751-ad8d-ffb7ff5a0000</link><description>空中渗透和火箭警报整个周六持续不断，以色列军队表示拦截了几个可疑目标，并使天露探测和警告气球重新投入运行。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 15:29:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-fires-large-rocket-salvo-in-initial-response-to-killing-of-hamas-leader/0000018c-df37-d751-ad8d-ffb7ff5a0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列国防军坦克在贝埃里家中丧生的以色列人家属要求调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israelis-killed-in-beeri-home-hit-by-tank-fire-on-october-7-demand-probe/0000018c-de77-daf6-a5df-df7f22d60000</link><description>遇难者家属表示，哈马斯关押在贝埃里一所房屋内的以色列人在与以色列国防军坦克交火中丧生，对这一事件的调查必须立即展开，而不是在战后展开。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 12:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israelis-killed-in-beeri-home-hit-by-tank-fire-on-october-7-demand-probe/0000018c-de77-daf6-a5df-df7f22d60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长的诽谤危及我们的安全——并呼吁采取施压行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-mudslinging-imperils-our-security-and-calls-for-a-pressure-campaign/0000018c-ddd1-daf6-a5df-dffd56780000</link><description>周五安全内阁会议上的惨败，右翼部长们对以色列国防军对其 10 月 7 日失误进行的内部调查进行了猛烈抨击，这是即将发生的事情的令人作呕的开胃菜</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 09:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-mudslinging-imperils-our-security-and-calls-for-a-pressure-campaign/0000018c-ddd1-daf6-a5df-dffd56780000</guid></item><item><title>“当时没有关于如何对待儿童人质的知识，所以我们编造了这个。我们决定不拥抱或问问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/there-was-no-info-on-treating-child-hostages-we-made-it-up-we-had-no-room-for-mistakes/0000018c-db93-d751-ad8d-ffb7c7090000</link><description>埃夫拉特·布隆-哈列夫博士和她的工作人员在抵达施耐德儿童医疗中心后立即接收了从哈马斯囚禁中解救出来的年轻人质，没有先例，没有固定的程序等待着他们。没有犯错的余地</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 05:23:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/there-was-no-info-on-treating-child-hostages-we-made-it-up-we-had-no-room-for-mistakes/0000018c-db93-d751-ad8d-ffb7c7090000</guid></item><item><title>人质获释：“许多女孩在哈马斯囚禁期间遭受严重性虐待”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-hezbollah-operational-hq-in-lebanon-hostage-families-arrive-in-qatar/0000018c-dc92-d751-ad8d-ffb6524b0000</link><description>真主党声称向上加利利发射火箭弹是对哈马斯领导人在贝鲁特被杀的“初步反应” ■ 以色列国防军袭击了从黎巴嫩发射火箭的小组 ■ 10 月 7 日在贝埃里家中被坦克炮火袭击而丧生的以色列人家属要求以色列国防军进行调查 ■ 在自10月7日以来，以色列境内至少有1,300名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 22,722 人死亡、58,166 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 02:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-hezbollah-operational-hq-in-lebanon-hostage-families-arrive-in-qatar/0000018c-dc92-d751-ad8d-ffb6524b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队中有人决定将这个安静的约旦河西岸地区带入暴力圈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/someone-in-the-idf-decided-to-bring-this-quiet-west-bank-area-into-the-circle-of-violence/0000018c-daf0-daf6-a5df-dffcc42c0000</link><description>一枚以色列国防军导弹射入约旦河西岸难民营中心，造成六名年轻人死亡，七人受伤。军队最初拒绝救护车进入现场，边防警察对伤员拳打脚踢。几天后，军队再次入侵营地</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 20:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/someone-in-the-idf-decided-to-bring-this-quiet-west-bank-area-into-the-circle-of-violence/0000018c-daf0-daf6-a5df-dffcc42c0000</guid></item><item><title>年龄：23​​岁；在以色列停留时间：25天；在加沙被扣为人质的时间：90多天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/age-23-time-in-israel-25-days-time-held-hostage-in-gaza-over-90-days/0000018c-d9c6-daf6-a5df-dffe5c260000</link><description>一连几天都没有比平·乔希的踪影。多亏了以色列国防军发布的加沙希法医院的一段视频，他在尼泊尔的家人才得知他被活着带到加沙。三个月后，他在大屠杀中幸存的朋友们重温了恐怖时刻，并参加了拯救他的活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:26:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/age-23-time-in-israel-25-days-time-held-hostage-in-gaza-over-90-days/0000018c-d9c6-daf6-a5df-dffe5c260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的失败主义者是哈马斯有用的白痴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-defeatists-are-hamas-useful-idiots/0000018c-dac9-ddba-abad-dae9a5d40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-defeatists-are-hamas-useful-idiots/0000018c-dac9-ddba-abad-dae9a5d40000</guid></item><item><title>犹太-阿拉伯伙伴关系正在以色列建立一个年轻的新和平营</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-jewish-arab-partnership-is-building-a-young-new-peace-camp-in-israel/0000018c-daa9-d751-ad8d-ffadd6e00000</link><description>在加沙战争中，“站在一起”组织进展顺利：它拥有 5,000 名缴纳会费的会员，其学生分会的数量增加了一倍，新的犹太人和阿拉伯人团体正在努力保持团结，并为共同生活注入希望在以色列</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 18:32:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-jewish-arab-partnership-is-building-a-young-new-peace-camp-in-israel/0000018c-daa9-d751-ad8d-ffadd6e00000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗官员试图将致命爆炸归咎于以色列和美国——即使伊斯兰国声称对此负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-pins-deadly-blasts-on-israel-and-u-s-despite-isis-claiming-responsibility/0000018c-dab5-ddba-abad-dab533f60000</link><description>伊朗指挥官表示，“他们只能充当美国政治和犹太复国主义的代理人和雇佣兵”，革命卫队发誓要对周三造成数十人死亡的自杀式爆炸袭击进行报复</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 18:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-pins-deadly-blasts-on-israel-and-u-s-despite-isis-claiming-responsibility/0000018c-dab5-ddba-abad-dab533f60000</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国在以色列-哈马斯战争中站在巴勒斯坦一边</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-china-is-siding-with-the-palestinians-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-da8d-ddba-abad-daad516d0000</link><description>中国的信息更多是针对华盛顿而不是耶路撒冷</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-china-is-siding-with-the-palestinians-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-da8d-ddba-abad-daad516d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>